quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  68,43,"Hara gite ma…ď…ďe …óeen no heli, koyeera no suddi …ďe. Ko tawde …ďe noddeteno e cujjugol fewndo ka …ďe mbaawunoo...!"
  68,44,"Accidam e kala jeddu…óo ndee yeewtere; aray nde Min suynira …ďe nokku ka …ďe nganndaa."
  68,45,"Mi…óo nee…ďnan …ďe. Pellet noon, pewje am …óen ko tii…ó…óe."
  68,46,"Kaa a la…ďndi …ďe njo…ďdi, hara ko yo…ďugol ndi teddani …ďe?"
  68,47,"Kaa …ďe nganndu fii wirnii…ói …óiin, hara hi…ďe mbinndira […óim hujjaaji ma…ď…ďe]?"
  68,48,"Mu√Ī√Īor √Īaawoore Joommaa nden, hara a wa'aali wa wonndii…óo linngii ngii fewndo o noddunoo [Joom makko] homo sunii."
  68,49,"Si tawno mo∆ī∆īere immorde e Joomi makko hewtitanooki mo, ko pellet, o bugeteno e wulaa hara ko o pelnii…óo."
  68,50,"Joomi makko su…ďii mo, o wa…ói mo e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďeen."
  68,51,"Hay yeddu…ďe …ďeen e…ď…ďiinoo yuwirgol ma gite ma…ď…ďe …óeen, nde …ďe nanunoo JaŇčtoore nden, hi…ďe mbi'a: "on ko kaangaa…óo!"."
  68,52,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waajo winndere nde!"
  69,1,"Darnga ngo."
  69,2,"Anndinat ma ko woni darnga?"
  69,3,"Ko hon…óum anndin maa ko woni Darngal?"
  69,4,"Samuudu e Aadi en njeddii du…ó…óugol Darnga."
  69,5,"Si ko Samuuda en, …ďe kalkira ha'acaango."
  69,6,"Aadi en kan, …ďe kalkira henndu bippooru hattinndu tii…óude."
  69,7,"O eelti ndu e hoore ma…ď…ďe jehmaaji jee…ói…ói e √Īalawmaaje jeetati jokkondir…óe; nji'aa yim…ďe …ďeen no pukkii e …óiin [ko…óooli] wa si tawii ko …ďe da∆ī∆īe tamaro irtii…óe."
  69,8,"Taw si a yi'anat …ďe ko keddii?"